.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Take necessary vaccines: vaccines are necessary for children and adults are advised to take it for the Prevention of infection, in addition to providing vaccines to be taken in case of travel to certain areas of the world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Shows the importance of vaccines in the Prevention of infections by encouraging the body to produce white blood cells and antibodies, which attack germs in the body not again.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>Practice safe sex: use of condoms one of the methods of prevention of foodborne disease the body.1] dealing with animals caution: there are many diseases that can be transmitted through animals, so you should pay attention when breeding household pets to review the vet to make sure their safety and give them the vaccines that are necessary, in addition to the need to organize its own zone, and to prevent children from borrowing the feces of these animals.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'How to prevent from diseases', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '76-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-31 22:47:36', '2019-12-31 22:47:36', '', 76, 'https://en.2fun.club/76-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
