ng your digestive tract to move food, stimulating your organs, and relieving the stress that partially causes bloating.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":498,"width":417,"height":511,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/535i.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-498" width="417" height="511"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whatever the time, you should never forget to hydrate your body.&nbsp;Water is actually a solution to many of the health problems you may be having, and one of them is bloating.&nbsp;Your daily consumption of water is supposed to be around 8 glasses and that doesn''t even count the other liquids you drink.&nbsp;So stay hydrated and your body will have all the power it needs to fight bloating.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '10 Solid Ways To Reduce Stomach Bloating.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '474-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-22 11:30:28', '2020-02-22 11:30:28', '', 474, 'https://en.2fun.club/474-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
