:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Skin rashes and itching may appear due to the buildup of waste products.&nbsp;As the waste builds up in the blood, the skin dries up and becomes irritated.&nbsp;This problem cannot be solved with creams and lotions because the root cause is internal and needs another approach.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>6. DURATION OF BREATHING</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This symptom can appear because of the low number of red blood cells, caused by a toxic build-up in the lungs, because it reduces the amount of oxygen in the body.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>7. OIL</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":532,"width":420,"height":236,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/front-view-cup-with-olive-oil-table_23-2148285939.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-532" width="420" height="236"/><figcaption>Freepik</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The excess fluids remain trapped in the body and lead to swelling if kidney function is compromised.&nbsp;This swelling appears on the face, limbs and joints in particular.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>8. CHANGES IN URINE</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are some of the most common signs:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Foamy<br>urine Urinary problems<br>Urination to urinate overnight&nbsp;Urine<br>pressure Dark urine, urine and urination less common in small amounts<br>Pale color, frequent urination, and in large amounts</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'If your kidney is in danger, the body will give you these 8 signs!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '520-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-02-24 17:30:48', '2020-02-24 17:30:48', '', 520, 'https://en.2fun.club/520-revision-v1/