d States by a group of people for 20 years, according to dietetik.ro.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The content in phytonutrients plays an antioxidant role, also helping to stabilize blood sugar levels by preventing the accumulation of sugar in the blood, making it a very useful food for people suffering from diabetes or hypoglycaemia.<ins></ins></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The fibers and proteins in the composition of this vegetable stabilize digestion and can be helpful in weight loss, a cup of 250 calories and provides 50% of the daily fiber needs and 30% of the protein needs.&nbsp;Insoluble fibers in the structure of the swab are extremely beneficial for combating constipation and controlling appetite, quickly producing a feeling of saturation, according to the site whfoods.org.&nbsp;These fibers are not absorbed into the intestines.&nbsp;It swells in the presence of water and cleanses the intestines.&nbsp;Being high in fiber, swimming helps reduce the risk of colon cancer</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Also, the birth is indicated in oliguria (insufficiency of the urinary secretion), infections of the urinary tract and urinary lithiasis, according to the site counseling.ro.<ins></ins></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Swimming is also recommended in physical and mental asthenia, and in convalescence, in the form of infusion, decoction, because it is a nutritious and diuretic food.&nbsp;Due to its tryptophan content and Vitamin B6, which is important for serotonin production, it may be useful to those with sleep disorders.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Due to the high folic acid content, birth is recommended for pregnant women and those who want to become mothers.&nbsp;The iron in the berries produces energy, and magnesium increases the amount of enzymes, which produce antioxidants that slow down the aging process.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The drinking water combats the cold and energizes.&nbsp;The swim is recommended for the treatment of colds, pharyngitis and neuralgia and in the form of gargle or poultice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Indian researchers have concluded that birth control could be the basis of treatment for millions of vitiligo patients worldwide.&nbsp;The study revealed that applying a nails ointment on the depigmented areas can effectively treat the disease, helping to repigment the skin and effectively controlling the spread of the disease.&nbsp;Research on a number of patients showed that they regained their pigment in a period of 20 to 90 days.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>People who have gout or have kidney problems should consult a nutritionist before consuming it, which also contains purines, which are harmful to those who suffer from such conditions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '610-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-03-11 17:23:12', '2020-03-11 17:23:12', '', 610, 'https://en.2fun.club/610-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
