(679, 1, '2020-03-18 13:19:45', '2020-03-18 13:19:45', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Studies&nbsp;have shown that different people may interpret what they see differently depending on&nbsp;their personalities. The eyes see everything but the brain picks what’s most important to&nbsp;you first. In&nbsp;this particular test, you’ll see what’s actually most valuable to&nbsp;you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We&nbsp;at&nbsp;Bright Side&nbsp;love quizzes and tests, but please remember it’s just a&nbsp;game&nbsp;— don’t take it&nbsp;too seriously! However, if&nbsp;you find that the results are spot&nbsp;on, maybe it’s not just a&nbsp;joke after all.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>1. What do&nbsp;you see first?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":690,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8796910-image-crop-1500x660-1545895712-728-cf5107f00b-1545987222.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-690"/><figcaption>© pixabay.com</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"vivid-red","backgroundColor":"vivid-green-cyan","customFontSize":80} -->\n<p style="font-size:80px" class="has-text-color has-background has-text-align-center has-vivid-red-color has-vivid-green-cyan-background-color"><em><strong>???</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Zebra:</strong>&nbsp;You’re an&nbsp;extrovert: you love talking, partying, meeting new people, and doing new things. Following a&nbsp;routine is&nbsp;not your style.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Lion:</strong>&nbsp;You’re an&nbsp;introvert: you like spending quality time alone or&nbsp;with the company of&nbsp;a&nbsp;loved one, a&nbsp;glass of&nbsp;your favorite drink, and a&nbsp;few episodes of&nbsp;your favorite&nbsp;TV show.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>2. What do&nbsp;you see first?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":691,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8795660-35668160-89d1fe9e00cda3b2517d8dd78577364d153097e5-2000-1-1545123241-728-32e9147584-1545987222.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-691"/><figcaption>© brightside.me</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[adinserter block="4"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"vivid-green-cyan","backgroundColor":"pale-pink","customFontSize":80} -->\n<p style="font-size:80px" class="has-text-color has-background has-text-align-center has-vivid-green-cyan-color has-pale-pink-background-color"><em><strong>???</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Tree:</strong>&nbsp;You can be&nbsp;a&nbsp;bit quiet but it’s not because you’re shy. You just like being who you are and don’t need anyone’s approval.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Gorilla:</strong>&nbsp;You’re a&nbsp;maximalist and a&nbsp;perfectionist. Just keep in&nbsp;mind that sometimes you might be&nbsp;too critical and it&nbsp;can hurt people.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Lioness:&nbsp;</strong>You have a&nbsp;very strong personality and don’t let anyone stand in&nbsp;your way.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Fish:</strong>&nbsp;You’re very sensitive and have a&nbsp;soft personality and caring heart. Don’t let other people take it&nbsp;for granted.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>3. What do&nbsp;you see first?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":692,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8796110-41417960-232e77add65f8e7531259b7b70a03d34efbd462c-2000-1-1545648716-728-32e9147584-1545987222.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-692"/><figcaption>© brightside.me</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"pale-cyan-blue","backgroundColor":"luminous-vivid-orange","customFontSize":80} -->\n<p style="font-size:80px" class="has-text-color has-background has-text-align-center has-pale-cyan-blue-color has-luminous-vivid-orange-background-color"><em><strong>???</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Baby:</strong>&nbsp;You like having time to&nbsp;yourself and shouldn’t feel guilty if&nbsp;you just don’t feel like going out. That’s okay, be&nbsp;yourself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Couple:</strong>&nbsp;You love your friends and although you don’t like loud parties and big groups, you have a&nbsp;few very close friends and you would do&nbsp;absolutely anything for them.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Trees:&nbsp;</strong>You have a&nbsp;very bubbly personality and you’re always open to&nbsp;new experiences. Change is&nbsp;not a&nbsp;big deal for you. In&nbsp;fact, you love change!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[adinserter block="3"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:nextpage -->\n<!--nextpage-->\n<!-- /wp:nextpage -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>4. What do&nbsp;you see first?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":693,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8796010-42542460-a99cec36b643422bac7a554d288ab1f8ae9088e9-2000-1-1545730607-728-32e9147584-1545987222.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-693"/><figcaption>© brightside.me</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"very-dark-gray","backgroundColor":"cyan-bluish-gray","customFontSize":80} -->\n<p style="font-size:80px" class="has-text-color has-background has-text-align-center has-very-dark-gray-color has-cyan-bluish-gray-background-color"><em><strong>???</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Trees:</strong>&nbsp;You have great intuition and always trust&nbsp;it. You have a&nbsp;very laid-back personality and like spending quiet time doing nothing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Tiger:</strong>&nbsp;“Don’t trouble the trouble if&nbsp;the trouble does not trouble you.” This saying is&nbsp;all about you! You have a&nbsp;very strong mind and once you make a&nbsp;decision, nothing can make you doubt that it&nbsp;was the right one.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>5. What do&nbsp;you see first?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":694,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8795910-40692610-56d9bf5153b2e16da42b10bc6a5a86908111517e-2000-1-1545585979-728-32e9147584-1545987222.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-694"/><figcaption>© brightside.me</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"luminous-vivid-orange","backgroundColor":"vivid-purple","customFontSize":80} -->\n<p style="font-size:80px" class="has-text-color has-background has-text-align-center has-luminous-vivid-orange-color has-vivid-purple-background-color"><em><strong>???</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Trees:</strong>&nbsp;Your endless energy is&nbsp;amazing. You’re spontaneous and are always ready to&nbsp;explore new places. You cannot possibly have 2&nbsp;days that are exactly the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[adinserter block="4"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Face:</strong>&nbsp;You like to&nbsp;have everything in&nbsp;order. Having every little thing well-planned and knowing what happens tomorrow, the next week, or&nbsp;even the next month makes you feel safe and comfortable.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>6. What do&nbsp;you see first?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":695,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8795810-42139760-8893fbc1f7ef92827ac96382c3e369d896d20512-2000-1-1545690561-728-32e9147584-1545987222.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-695"/><figcaption>© brightside.me</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"pale-cyan-blue","backgroundColor":"vivid-cyan-blue","customFontSize":80} -->\n<p style="font-size:80px" class="has-text-color has-background has-text-align-center has-pale-cyan-blue-color has-vivid-cyan-blue-background-color"><em><strong>???</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Saxophonist:</strong>&nbsp;You are a&nbsp;social butterfly and the center of&nbsp;every party. It’s no&nbsp;wonder that everyone wants to&nbsp;be&nbsp;your friend. Just don’t forget that every now and then, we&nbsp;all need a&nbsp;break to&nbsp;recharge.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Face:</strong>&nbsp;Big noisy parties are not for you. In&nbsp;fact, you often get really emotionally drained and physically exhausted from being in&nbsp;a&nbsp;large group of&nbsp;people for a&nbsp;long time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>7. What do&nbsp;you see first?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":696,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/8795710-42137760-55bad49c6e5a23dc3ccbcfa09cc4ccdc7d77832f-2000-1-1545690120-728-32e9147584-1545987222.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-696"/><figcaption>© brightside.me</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center","textColor":"vivid-red","backgroundColor":"very-dark-gray","customFontSize":80} -->\n<p style="font-size:80px" class="has-text-color has-background has-text-align-center has-vivid-red-color has-very-dark-gray-background-color"><em><strong>???</strong></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Face:</strong>&nbsp;You are very down to&nbsp;earth, easy to&nbsp;talk&nbsp;to, understanding, and sincerely caring.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2&nbsp;figures:</strong>&nbsp;You’re very competitive and it&nbsp;applies to&nbsp;everything, not just sports or&nbsp;work. Whatever you&nbsp;do, you just have to&nbsp;be&nbsp;the best. It’s great setting high goals but remember, even the best of&nbsp;us need rest.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Did we get it right? Either way, tell us about your results in the comments and share this article with your friends and family.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[adinserter block="3"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->', 'The First Image You See Can Reveal What Your Heart Longs For Most', '', 'private', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-first-image-you-see-can-reveal-what-your-heart-longs-for-most', '', '', '2020-03-28 14:01:27', '2020-03-28 14:01:27', '', 0, 'https://en.2fun.club/?p=679', 0, 'post', '', 0),
