>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The lemon''s cleansing reputation is certainly not stolen.&nbsp;And for good reason, the citrus fruit fights against toxins with its arms through its vitamin C. We also need the stimulating mechanisms of the immune system thanks to the latter, a scientific assertion confirmed by this&nbsp;&nbsp;study&nbsp;.&nbsp;Reason enough to press more often on our seasonal salads and morning smoothies!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[adinserter block="3"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:nextpage -->\n<!--nextpage-->\n<!-- /wp:nextpage -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>2-&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>The red pepper</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":828,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pexels-photo-1091778.jpeg" alt="" class="wp-image-828"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This spicy food deserves to be consumed more often.&nbsp;The reason ?&nbsp;It improves the performance of our natural defenses, an essential activity to fight against pathogens and viruses.&nbsp;And&nbsp;&nbsp;scientists&nbsp;&nbsp;do not budge since according to this community the red pepper has proven anti-inflammatory effects.&nbsp;More reasons then not to enhance the taste of these dishes with this ingredient.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[adinserter block="4"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>3-&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Citrus</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":830,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pexels-photo-1414131.jpeg" alt="" class="wp-image-830"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Like lemon, citrus fruits are also natural remedies to activate your immune system.&nbsp;It is&nbsp;&nbsp;scientifically&nbsp;&nbsp;proven: this category of food improves this function, and in particular contributes to an effective resistance against the disease of the dark spots.&nbsp;A convincing argument to always have these acidic fruits in your basket!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>4-&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Turmeric</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":832,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pexels-photo-877220.jpeg" alt="" class="wp-image-832"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A sacred spice in the East, Indian saffron is one of the essential foods to promote better immunity.&nbsp;<em>Turmeric loin</em>&nbsp;, its Latin name, can improve antibody responses.&nbsp;It also acts as a powerful immunomodulatory agent but also inhibits inflammatory reactions.&nbsp;A property confirmed by this&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;scientific&nbsp;study&nbsp;.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[adinserter block="3"]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode -->\n\n<!-- wp:nextpage -->\n<!--nextpage-->\n<!-- /wp:nextpage -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>5-&nbsp;Spinach</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {"id":835,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/pexels-photo-1751149.jpeg" alt="" class="wp-image-835"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>These leafy plants benefit from being consumed more often.&nbsp;And it is a highly sought-after property that we recognize since they are rich in beta-carotene and vitamin C, ideal for boosting your immune system.&nbsp;According to this&nbsp;&nbsp;study&nbsp;, Popeye''s favorite foods are recommended to combat the presence of&nbsp;&nbsp;viruses&nbsp;&nbsp;and pathogens.&nbsp;No need to hesitate to add more to your balanced dishes!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n