(876, 1, '2020-04-23 12:25:59', '2020-04-23 12:25:59', '<!-- wp:image {"id":875,"sizeSlug":"large"} -->\n<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img src="https://en.2fun.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/dark-1839088_1280-1024x682.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-875"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>   &nbsp;You train to be fit.&nbsp; Thus, for your training to remain effective and safe, some mistakes should be avoided in a gym.&nbsp; Here are seven of the most common ones.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>&nbsp;1. Do not hydrate yourself enough:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp; You are not thirsty?&nbsp; You must drink anyway.&nbsp; Indeed, if you feel thirsty, it is because you are already dehydrated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Proper hydration before, during and after training is essential to get enough energy and to provide the muscles with the nutrients they need. So, drink a few sips of water regularly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>&nbsp;2. Do not eat properly:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;If you do not eat enough, or if you train right after a meal, your performance will be affected.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Be sure to give your body all the nutrients it needs and eat at least two hours before you train.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>&nbsp;3. To be poorly equipped:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;To avoid pain, discomfort and possible injury, you must equip yourself properly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Quality shoes are needed for running, and the sports bra is an essential accessory for any woman who trains.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>&nbsp;4. Do not warm up:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Even if you have little time to train, do not neglect the warm up.&nbsp; Your body must adapt to physical effort.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Sudden rest from exercise often leads to muscle injury.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>&nbsp;5. Always do the same routine:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;To improve your results, you should change your routine every four weeks.&nbsp; After a while, the body gets used to the training program.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;If it means that you are in better shape, it also means that you have to increase the intensity of your exercises to continue to progress.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>&nbsp;6. Adopt the wrong program:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;One of the mistakes to avoid at the gym is to randomly choose your workout program.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Ask a coach to prepare a tailor made program and make sure you perform each exercise according to the correct technique.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->\n<h3>&nbsp;7. Do not listen to your body:</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Do you have pain or cramps?&nbsp; Take a break.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;If you are too exhausted to train, it is better to stay at home, otherwise you may be injured.Attention, however, not to confuse psychological fatigue and physical fatigue.It is normal that your mind is tired after a day in the office,&nbsp; but if you have been sitting for hours, your body needs to move.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;Stay motivated!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;One last mistake to avoid in a gym: do not fall into excess.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;When you start training, you often want to do too much.&nbsp; If you train every day, training may become a chore rather than a pleasure and you will soon find it difficult to motivate yourself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', '7 mistakes to avoid at the gym', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '58-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-04-23 12:25:59', '2020-04-23 12:25:59', '', 58, 'https://en.2fun.club/58-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
